{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d802aab5ad","title":"为登载两篇文艺理论文章写的编者按","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e5322a5eaa","index":0,"year":1964,"month":7,"day":7,"articleId":"d802aab5ad"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"92a8a42842","name":"姚文元","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"a990f4689e","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d802aab5ad","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"姚文元，当时任上海解放日报社编委兼文艺部主任。14]周谷城，当时是复旦大学教授。他写的文章的题目为《统一整体与分别反映》（载1963年11月7日《光明日报》）。"}],"contents":[{"id":"86771dba6a","type":"title","text":"为登载两篇文艺理论文章写的编者按！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d802aab5ad"},{"id":"a990f4689e","type":"paragraph","text":"这两篇文章，可以一读。一篇是姚文元驳周谷城的，另一篇是支持周谷城反驳姚文元的。都是涉及文艺理论问题的。文艺工作者应当懂得一点文艺理论，否则会迷失放（方）向。这两篇批判文章不难读。究竟谁的论点较为正确，由读者自己考虑。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d802aab5ad"},{"id":"8326d15649","type":"paragraph","text":"编者","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d802aab5ad"},{"id":"8a806fd312","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年七月七日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d802aab5ad"},{"id":"f685e75018","type":"paragraph","text":"[i]这个编者按后来没有发表。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d802aab5ad"},{"id":"24a5fb8d7f","type":"paragraph","text":"指姚文元写的《评周谷城先生的矛盾观》（载1964年5月10日《光明日报》）和金为民、李云初写的《关于时代精神的几点疑问》（载1964年7月7日《光明日报》）。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d802aab5ad"}],"page":{"id":"566f4823fd","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d802aab5ad","start":473,"end":473}}}},"__N_SSG":true}